(114,	'Announcement',	0,	'La Journée internationale de la physique médicale',	'International Day of Medical Physics',	'<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;float: none;\">L\'unité de Physique médicale organisera une célébration de la Journée </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;float: none;\">internationale de la physique médicale dans la salle de conférence RBC </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;float: none;\">du Centre du cancer des Cèdres, le jeudi 8 novembre à 14 heures. Tout </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;float: none;\">le monde est le bienvenu. Venez rencontrer l\'équipe qui a développé </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;float: none;\">l\'application Opal !</span><!--EndFragment--><br/><br/><img src=\"https://docs.google.com/drawings/d/e/2PACX-1vRnL6lnUH3laBnH8pbkxKb-SL29X_OgvW7hHxuQSCqYU52iq-khaaayON7kYQEhaHWbMvByKy_jNr1i/pub?w=864&amp;h=384\"/><br/></p>',	'<p>The Medical Physics Unit will host an International Day of Medical Physics celebration in the RBC Conference room of the Cedars Cancer Centre at 2 pm on Thursday November 8th. Everyone welcome. Come meet the team that developed the Opal app!<br/><br/><img src=\"https://docs.google.com/drawings/d/e/2PACX-1vRnL6lnUH3laBnH8pbkxKb-SL29X_OgvW7hHxuQSCqYU52iq-khaaayON7kYQEhaHWbMvByKy_jNr1i/pub?w=864&amp;h=384\"/><br/></p>',	'2018-11-07 01:36:00',	0,	'2018-11-06 23:31:35',	'2019-05-21 18:18:02',	3,	'2019-05-22 02:19:56',	0,	'f0HPOkYvTx'),
(117,	'Announcement',	0,	'FERMETURE DE L’ÉCHANGEUR TURCOT du 9 au 13 novembre',	'TURCOT closed from November 9-13',	'<h1><strong>FERMETURE DE L’ÉCHANGEUR TURCOT du 9 au 13 novembre</strong></h1><p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Des fermetures sans précédent seront en place dans l’échangeur Turcot du 9 au 13 novembre prochains. Des conditions de circulation très difficiles sont à prévoir sur le réseau autoroutier durant cette période.</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://muhc.ca/sites/default/files/news/Press-releases/Map_Fr.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>',	'<h1><strong>TURCOT closed from November 9-13</strong></h1><p style=\"font-size: 14px;\">There will be unprecedented road closures in the Turcot interchange from November 9 to 13. Adverse traffic conditions are to be expected on the freeway network over this period.</p><div><img src=\"https://muhc.ca/sites/default/files/news/Press-releases/Map_En.jpg\"/><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><p><br/></p>',	'2018-11-07 18:00:00',	0,	'2018-11-07 17:58:19',	'2019-05-21 18:19:01',	3,	'2019-05-22 02:20:54',	0,	'f0HPOkYvTx'),
(118,	'Announcement',	0,	'Vos commentaires sont demandés',	'Your feedback is requested',	'<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">Bonjour usager d\'Opal,</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\"> </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">Nous avons été invités à fournir à l\'administration du Centre du cancer des Cèdres les commentaires des patients concernant le projet pilote Opal. Étant donné que vous êtes l’un de nos premiers patients, vos commentaires sur Opal sont très importants.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\"> </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">Nous avons créé un court sondage sur votre expérience avec Opal. Il est maintenant disponible dans la section </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\"><i>Questionnaires</i></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\"> d\'Opal sous l’onglet </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\"><i>Dossier</i></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">. Nous vous serions reconnaissants de bien vouloir prendre quelques minutes pour répondre à nos questions.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\"> </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">Toutes vos réponses resteront anonymes, mais vous pouvez nous laisser votre adresse courriel si vous le souhaitez.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">En plus de remplir le questionnaire dans l\'application, nous vous invitons à nous envoyer des commentaires et questions supplémentaires, si vous en avez, à opal@muhc.mcgill.ca.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\"> </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\"> </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #222222;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">En vous remerciant d’avance,</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">John, Laurie et Tarek, co-responsables de l\'équipe de développement Opal</span></p><!--EndFragment--><p><a href=\"http://opalmedapps.com/\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;background-color: transparent;text-decoration: underline;vertical-align: baseline;\">opalmedapps.com</span></a></p><!--EndFragment--><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>',	'<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;font-size: 11pt;\">Dear Opal user,</span><br/></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">We have been asked to provide patient feedback regarding the Opal pilot project to the administration of the Cedars Cancer Centre. As you are an early-adopter patient, your feedback regarding Opal is very important.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">We have created a short survey regarding your experience with Opal. It is now available within the Questionnaires section of Opal in the My Chart menu. We would really appreciate it if you could please take a few minutes to provide your responses.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">All responses will be kept anonymous but you may leave your email address if you wish.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\"> </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">In addition to completing the questionnaire in the app, we would welcome further comments or questions by e-mail at opal@muhc.mcgill.ca</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">Thank you very much,</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #000000;background-color: transparent;vertical-align: baseline;\">John, Laurie and Tarek, co-leads of the Opal development team</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"http://opalmedapps.com/\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;color: #1155cc;background-color: transparent;text-decoration: underline;vertical-align: baseline;\">opalmedapps.com</span></a></p><!--EndFragment--><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>',	'2018-11-23 14:30:00',	0,	'2018-11-23 14:19:35',	'2019-05-21 18:20:01',	3,	'2019-05-22 02:21:06',	0,	'f0HPOkYvTx'),
