calls, to keep in touch with family and friends through online dinners and games.</li><li>Work from home.</li><li>On your own property only: go outside on your balcony or deck, walk in your yard.</li></ul><p></p><p></p><p><u>Reminder of good practices:</u></p><ul><li>Keep your hands clean.</li><li>Wash your hands often with soap and water for at least 20 seconds, and dry with disposable paper towels or dry reusable towel, replacing it when it becomes wet.</li><li>You can also remove dirt with a wet wipe and then use an alcohol-based hand sanitizer.</li><li>Avoid touching your eyes, nose and mouth.</li><li>Cough or sneeze into the bend of your arm or into a tissue.</li><li>Keep surfaces clean.</li><li>Do not share personal items with others, such as toothbrushes, towels, bed linen, non-medical masks, utensils or electronic devices.</li></ul><p></p><p></p><p><u>Monitor yourself for symptoms:</u></p><ul><li>Monitor yourself for symptoms, particularly fever and respiratory symptoms such as coughing or difficulty breathing.</li><li>Take and record your temperature daily and avoid using fever-reducing medications (e.g. acetaminophen, ibuprofen) as much as possible. These medications could mask an early symptom of COVID-19.</li></ul><p></p><p><b>IF YOU HAVE ANY COUGH, FEVER OR FLU-LIKE SYMPTOMS (new onset within the last 7 days of sore throat, shortness of breath or difficulty breathing, nasal congestion and runny nose, new onset of diarrhea, a sudden headache or sudden loss of smell) PLEASE DO NOT COME TO YOUR TREATMENT AND CALL THIS NUMBER: 514-934-1934 x 43400</b></p><p></p>',	'2020-04-15 19:00:00',	0,	'2020-04-15 18:15:01',	'2021-09-30 00:56:01',	19,	'2021-09-30 09:04:26',	0,	'CfqQr7POHT'),
(202,	'Treatment Team Message',	0,	'Information importante concernant le stationnement',	'Important information regarding parking',	'<p>Prenez note que nous avons été avisé par le service à la clientèle du stationnement du CUSM que des frais s\\\'appliqueront pour le stationnement P1 Express à compter du 11 mai 2020. Le stationnement vous est offert sans frais jusqu\\\'au 10 mai 2020.<br/> <br/>Référez vous au document &#34;<a href=\\\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Tartf7WRskfwRIz2gtflgmDq26tEVxBBWn3TebNrJhw/edit?usp=sharing\\\" target=\\\"\\\">Stationnement réservé aux patients du Département de radio-oncologie du CUSM durant la pandémie COVID-19</a>&#34; pour plus d\\\'information sur le paiement du stationnement. <br/> <br/>Merci. <br/></p>',	'<p>Please note that we have been advised by the MUHC customer service parking office that fees will apply for parking in the P1 Express Lot as of May 11, 2020. Free parking continues until May 10, 2020.<br/> <br/>Refer to the document &#34;<a href=\\\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1mb727wvESyPrfXqfeiCsmoihrzVMSrBL04J0WYlKFm8/edit?usp=sharing\\\" target=\\\"\\\">Dedicated Parking for MUHC Radiation Oncology Patients during the COVID-19 Pandemic</a>&#34; for more information on payment options for parking. <br/> <br/>Thank you.<br/><br/></p>',	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	0,	'2020-05-05 13:03:02',	'2002-01-01 00:00:00',	8,	'2020-05-05 22:18:15',	1,	'2ofkOZGIIg'),
