ium;float: none;\\\">You will soon receive a notification with a report summarizing your responses for each questionnaire. Please keep in mind that this report is part of the e-IMPAQc research study and is not a replacement for an open discussion with your healthcare professional.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">For information related to COVID-19, you can visit the pages</span><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/covid-19/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"> COVID-19</a><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\"> and </span><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/covid-anxiety/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">COVID-19 Anxiety</a><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">We hope you will find the information suggested to you helpful. Please do not hesitate to contact us if you have any questions or comments at e-impaqc@mcgill.ca.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><!--EndFragment--><br/><br/><br/></p>',	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	0,	'2021-07-14 09:27:35',	'2021-09-30 00:56:01',	72,	'2021-09-30 09:04:26',	0,	'88hmM9osSb'),
