(754,	'Treatment Team Message',	1,	'Message from e-IMPAQc Treating Team - Reminder to complete Questionnaires 09-01-2021',	'Message from e-IMPAQc Treating Team - Reminder to complete Questionnaires 09-01-2021',	'<p><br/><br/><!--StartFragment--><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">This is a friendly reminder to complete your e-IMPAQc questionnaires before your next medical appointment with your doctor. Please complete them entirely before your scheduled appointment time to ensure your answers will be reviewed by your physician, as they WILL NOT be reviewed after the appointment time.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><!--EndFragment--><br/><br/><br/></p>',	'<p><br/><br/><!--StartFragment--><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">This is a friendly reminder to complete your e-IMPAQc questionnaires before your next medical appointment with your doctor. Please complete them entirely before your scheduled appointment time to ensure your answers will be reviewed by your physician, as they WILL NOT be reviewed after the appointment time.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><!--EndFragment--><br/><br/><br/></p>',	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	0,	'2021-09-01 07:23:15',	'2021-09-30 00:56:01',	72,	'2021-09-30 09:04:26',	0,	'u1jR1EFTSM'),
(755,	'Treatment Team Message',	1,	'Message from e-IMPAQc treating team - Moderate Symptom(s) Reported 09-01-2021',	'Message from e-IMPAQc treating team - Moderate Symptom(s) Reported 09-01-2021',	'<p><br/><br/><!--StartFragment--><br style=\\\"font-size: 14px;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">Thank you for completing the e-IMPAQc questionnaires. You have reported at least one symptom of moderate severity. Your answers will be reviewed by your physician shortly, and we recommend that you speak to them about your symptoms today.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">Tips on how to talk to your healthcare team can be found </span><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/talking-to-your-healthcare-team/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">here</a><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">The following links are additional resources on how to adequately manage your symptoms of concern:</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/sleep/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">Sleep</a><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/sexual-matters/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14px;\\\">Sexual Matters</a><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/understand-illness/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">Understanding my Illness or treatment</a><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">These symptom management resources and many more can also be found by visiting the website <a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/managing-symptoms/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\">e-IMPAQc.com</a>, or by tapping on the Education tab at the bottom of your screen. In the search field, type in the name of the symptom of concern, i.e., fatigue, and it will appear at the top of the list.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">You will soon receive a notification with a report summarizing your responses for each questionnaire. Please keep in mind that this report is part of the e-IMPAQc research study and is not a replacement for an open discussion with your healthcare professional.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">For information related to COVID-19, you can visit the pages </span><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/covid-19/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">COVID-19</a><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\"> and </span><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/covid-anxiety/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">COVID-19 Anxiety.</a><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\"></span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">We hope you will find the information suggested to you helpful. Please do not hesitate to contact us if you have any questions or comments at e-impaqc@mcgill.ca.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><!--EndFragment--><br/><br/><br/></p>',	'<p><br/><br/><!--StartFragment--><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">Thank you for completing the e-IMPAQc questionnaires. You have reported at least one symptom of moderate severity. Your answers will be reviewed by your physician shortly, and we recommend that you speak to them about your symptoms today.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">Tips on how to talk to your healthcare team can be found </span><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/talking-to-your-healthcare-team/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">here</a><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">The following links are additional resources on how to adequately manage your symptoms of concern:</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/sleep/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">Sleep</a><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/sexual-matters/\\\" target=\\\"\\\">Sexual Matters</a><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/understand-illness/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"><span id=\\\"selectionBoundary_1630504180580_3392536417313776\\\" class=\\\"rangySelectionBoundary\\\">&#65279;</span>Understanding my Illness or treatment</a><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">These symptom management resources and many more can also be found by visiting the website <a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/managing-symptoms/\\\" target=\\\"\\\">e-IMPAQc.com</a>, or by tapping on the Education tab at the bottom of your screen. In the search field, type in the name of the symptom of concern, i.e., fatigue, and it will appear at the top of the list.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">You will soon receive a notification with a report summarizing your responses for each questionnaire. Please keep in mind that this report is part of the e-IMPAQc research study and is not a replacement for an open discussion with your healthcare professional.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">For information related to COVID-19, you can visit the pages </span><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/covid-19/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">COVID-19</a><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\"> and </span><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/covid-anxiety/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">COVID-19 Anxiety.</a><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\"></span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">We hope you will find the information suggested to you helpful. Please do not hesitate to contact us if you have any questions or comments at e-impaqc@mcgill.ca.</span><br style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"/><!--EndFragment--><br/><br/><br/></p>',	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	0,	'2021-09-01 09:53:01',	'2021-09-30 00:56:01',	72,	'2021-09-30 09:04:26',	0,	'YgNN7tiqaW'),
(756,	'Treatment Team Message',	0,	'Message de l\'équipe de soins e-IMPAQc- Symptômes Sévères Rapportés 09-08-2021',	'Message de l\'équipe de soins e-IMPAQc- Symptômes Sévères Rapportés 09-08-2021',	'<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><!--StartFragment--><p><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">Merci d’avoir rempli les questionnaires e-IMPAQc. Vous avez rapporté au moins un symptôme de sévérité modérée. Vos réponses seront bientôt revues par votre médecin, et nous vous recommandons de lui parler de vos symptômes lors de votre rendez-vous aujourd’hui.</span></p><p><br style=\\\"font-size: 14px;\\\"/></p><p style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">Des conseils sur la communication avec votre équipe de soins peuvent être retrouvés <a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/fr/talking-to-your-healthcare-team/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\">ici</a>.<br/><br/>Les liens électroniques suivant sont des ressources additionnelles pour vous aider dans la gestion de vos symptômes :<br/><a href=\\\"http://e-impaqc.com/fr/tiredness/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\">Fatigue</a><br/><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/fr/anxiety/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\">Anxiété</a><br/><a href=\\\"http://e-impaqc.com/fr/depression/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\">Dépression</a><br/><a href=\\\"http://e-impaqc.com/fr/frustration/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\">Frustration et Colere</a><br/><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/fr/body-image/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\">Image Corporelle</a><br/></p><p style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">Ces ressources d’autogestion peuvent aussi être retrouvés sur <a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/fr/managing-symptoms/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\">e-impaqc.com</a>, ou en appuyant sur l’onglet “Éducation” sur l\\\'application en bas de votre écran. Dans le champ de recherche, tapez le symptôme d’intérêt, e.g., fatigue, et il apparaitra au haut de la page.<br/><br/>Vous recevrez bientôt une notification pour un rapport résumant vos réponses aux questionnaires. Toutefois, veuillez garder à l’esprit que ce rapport fait partie de l’étude e-IMPAQc et ne remplace pas vos discussions avec votre professionnel de la santé.<br/><br/>Pour des informations sur la COVID-19, visitez les pages<a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/fr/covid-19/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\"> COVID-19</a> et <a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/fr/covid-anxiety/\\\" target=\\\"\\\" style=\\\"background-color: transparent;\\\">COVID-19 Anxiété</a>.<br/><br/>Nous espérons que les informations proposées vous seront utiles. N\\\'hésitez pas à nous contacter si vous avez des questions ou des commentaires à l\\\'adresse e-impaqc@mcgill.ca.</p><!--EndFragment--><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>',	'<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><!--StartFragment--><p><span style=\\\"font-size: medium;float: none;\\\">Merci d’avoir rempli les questionnaires e-IMPAQc. Vous avez rapporté au moins un symptôme de sévérité modérée. Vos réponses seront bientôt revues par votre médecin, et nous vous recommandons de lui parler de vos symptômes lors de votre rendez-vous aujourd’hui.</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\"></p><p style=\\\"font-size: medium;\\\">Des conseils sur la communication avec votre équipe de soins peuvent être retrouvés <a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/fr/talking-to-your-healthcare-team/\\\" target=\\\"\\\">ici</a>.<br/><br/>Les liens électroniques suivant sont des ressources additionnelles pour vous aider dans la gestion de vos symptômes :<br/><a href=\\\"http://e-impaqc.com/fr/tiredness/\\\" target=\\\"\\\">Fatigue</a><br/><a href=\\\"https://e-impaqc.com/fr/anxiety/\\\" target=\\\"\\\">Anxiété</a><br/><a href=\\\"http://e-impaqc.com/fr/depression/\\\" target=\\\"\\\">Dépression</a><br/><a href=\\\"http://e-impaqc.com